data.text:
Pitt Business Dean’s List – Spring 2024

The Pitt Business Dean’s List recognizes exemplary academic performance by our students.

The requirements for the Spring 2024 Dean’s List were:

At least 12 earned credits

Term GPA of at least 3.50

No grade lower than a C (this includes NC grades)

We are proud of our outstanding students and congratulate them on their accomplishments in going From the Classroom, To the City, To the World.
